snippet.title: This is the FIRST Boss! -Super Mario Star World-
snippet.description:
The Star Road 2 plan has been in progress for quite a long time, and I had intended to keep it secret for players to eventually discover on their own - however, this has lead to difficulty in reporting game development progress, and is a bit too significant not to use as a selling point for the game.
